	<p style="text-align: justify;">}</p>
	<p style="text-align: justify;">
		&nbsp;<strong>Step 5 : Passing value in Chain using
			ContextBase</strong>
	</p>
	<p style="text-align: justify;">
		<strong>&nbsp;</strong>As discussed in previous ,ContextBase
		initialize the contents of this&nbsp;<a
			href="http://commons.apache.org/proper/commons-chain/apidocs/org/apache/commons/chain/Context.html">Context</a>&nbsp;by
		copying the values from the specified&nbsp;Map. Any keys
		in&nbsp;map&nbsp;that correspond to local properties will cause the
