	<h3 style="text-align: justify;">Limitation</h3>
	<p style="text-align: justify;">Chain is not a full workflow
		system. It does not have sophisticated flow of control between
		branches of chains or looping. However, it is also easier to get
		started with than most workflow systems and you can easily refactor
		existing code to fit within it. Editing the XML file to change the
		sequence of commands or alter the parameters passed to a command is
		also well within the realm of what many end users can do themselves
		without minimal instruction.</p>
